    %h2 What Will You Learn?

    %p
        By the end of the course you will be able to create 
        %strong web-based applications
        from scratch.
    %p You will have enough knowledge to develop and expand your skills without further tuition.
    
    %p On each day, we will focus on creating a whole application.
    
    %h3 Saturday - An Online CV
    %p You will create a personal CV similar to the one shown on the right. By the end of the day, you will be able to reproduce this from scratch, by yourself.
    
